---
const faqs = [
  {
    question: 'What is OnThisDay.PH?',
    answer: 'OnThisDay.PH is a civic tech platform that presents Philippine history in meme format with verified sources — covering everything from political milestones to cultural achievements, disasters, and sports.',
  },
  {
    question: 'Is it free to use?',
    answer: 'Yes! OnThisDay.PH is completely free. Anyone can view, submit, and share historical entries.',
  },
  {
    question: 'How are sources verified?',
    answer: 'Every submission requires linked sources — news articles, government records, academic publications. The community votes on the accuracy and reliability of each entry.',
  },
  {
    question: 'Can I submit my own historical events?',
    answer: 'Absolutely. Sign up on the app and submit any Philippine historical event with a meme and supporting sources. The community will review and verify it.',
  },
  {
    question: 'Is this only about politics?',
    answer: 'Not at all. OnThisDay.PH covers all significant Filipino moments — sports achievements, cultural milestones, natural disasters, scientific breakthroughs, and more. If it matters to Filipinos, it belongs here.',
  },
  {
    question: 'How can I contribute to the project?',
    answer: 'Submit historical events on the app, help verify existing entries, or simply share verified history with your network. Every contribution helps preserve the truth.',
  },
];
---

<section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 animate-on-scroll">
      <p class="text-sm font-bold text-ph-blue uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">FAQ</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Everything you need to know about using and contributing to OnThisDay.PH.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-3">
      {faqs.map(faq => (
        <details class="group bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:border-gray-300 transition-colors animate-on-scroll">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer p-5 font-semibold text-gray-900 hover:text-ph-blue transition-colors">
            <span class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 group-hover:text-ph-blue transition-colors shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.228 9c.549-1.165 2.03-2 3.772-2 2.21 0 4 1.343 4 3 0 1.4-1.278 2.575-3.006 2.907-.542.104-.994.54-.994 1.093m0 3h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
              {faq.question}
            </span>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform shrink-0 ml-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-5 pb-5 pl-13 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            {faq.answer}
          </div>
        </details>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
